Description:
If Privacy Is Your Style
This country lifestyle property positioned right next to Keilor village, flanked by the Maribyrnong River offers a tranquil setting to balance a busy lifestyle. Set on 6.25 acres approx the property planted with 350 Arbiquina olive trees could be utilised as a great hobby farm. The original homestead and existing home are situated to take advantage of views over the river and down the valley. 2 bedrooms with BIR's, lounge, central bathroom and large verandah. Add to this a secure gated entry, water pumping facilities (12 meg pumping allocation), town water, easy access to Keilor village, Calder Highway, Melbourne Airport and the CBD.

Description:
Enjoy Welcoming And Bright Family Living A Short Walk To Keilor Village
With a choice of welcoming and bright family spaces, a spacious lounge room with a gorgeously cosy fire place opens onto a private deck, creating a space equally perfect for relaxed winter nights or balmy summer days. An inviting formal dining room, set off by beautiful half-timber walls leads you to the excellent kitchen with a casual dining area and picturesque views of the gardens opening to a second outdoor covered deck, perfect all year round. Enjoy long dinner parties with friends, relaxing mornings reading the paper, or festive summer barbeques in this superbly versatile zone perfect for celebrating any occasion. A stylish main suite is a tranquil and relaxed retreat, with a sleek ensuite and walk in robe and enjoying serene garden views and convenient direct garden access. Three further bright bedrooms (BIRs) all share a spacious and sparkling central bathroom with luxurious spa bath. The established rear gardens, frequented by many native birds, offer an excellent private oasis. With dual carport, split system air conditioning and ducted heating, walk to Keilor Village and Keilor Primary School whilst Overnewton College is nearby.

Description:
TERRIFIC INDOOR/OUTDOOR FAMILY LIVING!
With its versatile design, added extras and terrific poolside entertaining area, this pristine 4BR home offers an instantly enjoyable lifestyle with plenty of scope to modernize in the future. Perfectly presented throughout, the home features three upstairs bedrooms (large master with WIR and ensuite), main family bathroom and central rumpus/study area. Downstairs: fourth bedroom and additional powder room, formal lounge and dining, kitchen/meals and spacious rear living room complete with wet-bar. Other highlights include ducted heating and split-system air conditioning, solar power, separate laundry and internally-accessed double garage, second driveway, plus a north-facing backyard with undercover entertaining area, in-ground pool and additional (third) bathroom, workshop/studio and garden shed. Conveniently positioned with parkland across the road, it's walking distance to St Augustine's Primary School and Overnewton College, plus easy access to Keilor Village shops, public transport and Calder Freeway.

Description:
UNDOUBTEDLY ONE OF MELBOURNE'S FINEST MODERN HOMES
A new benchmark in luxury family living, this Marie Bagnato-designed 6BR masterpiece delivers an indoor/outdoor lifestyle of incomparable quality, opulence and family flexibility on over 2700sqm of land. With towering ceilings and the finest fittings and materials throughout, the home's expansive single-level floorplan boasts a stunning master suite with retreat, fully-fitted dressing room and deluxe private bathroom, separate kids' wing featuring four additional bedrooms (all with WIRs, study desks and ensuites) and central rumpus area, guest bedroom and bathroom, superb home office. Multiple living zones include entertaining/billiard room with full bar and wine storage, vast open-plan living/dining area complemented by a marble-bench kitchen with integrated fridges, all-Miele appliances and butlers' pantry, plus a family-sized laundry (with drying room), study/playroom with workstations, four-car showroom garage and additional two car garage via side driveway complete with turntable. Other features include commercial-grade heating and cooling throughout, in-slab heating, Travertine floors and walls, automated blinds and lighting systems, integrated audio, alarm and video intercom. Step outside to a stunning al-fresco entertaining area with outdoor kitchen, purpose-built gymnasium and indoor heated pool and spa, full-sized tennis court, Paul Bangay-designed gardens all-round. Executive living at its absolute finest ideally positioned in the heart of Keilor Village a truly once-in-a-lifetime opportunity! For the discerning and qualified buyers please contact:
Peter Weda 0419 767 803 or
Conjunctional agency Nelson Alexander:
David Vaughan 0418 231 290
